data.name: dataset.nusignals-transaction-lead-time-thub-daily
data.description:
This dataset process the lead time metrics for transactions
categorized by NuSignals taking as parameters: the summary
interval (daily, weekly, monthly), the date field to be used
and the aggregation type (per_product).
